dc_title_s: South America, Venezuela, Península de Paraguaná, Punta Salinas to Punta Cardón (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by form lines, hachures, and spot heights. "From U.S. and Venezuela charts to 1990." "Copyright 2007 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Inset: Bahía Boca de las Piedras. Scale 1:10,000. Includes source diagram and tidal information. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 24471. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
